data.chText: 把（违法者或无合法居留权的人）驱逐出境，递解出境
data.enText: to force sb to leave a country, usually because they have broken the law or because they have no legal right to be there

data.chText: 寻求避难的人中有几个将遭递解出境。
data.enText: Several of the asylum seekers now face deportation.

simple_means.memory_skill: de 去掉 + port 拿，运 → 拿出去 → 放逐

means: 把(违法者或无合法居留权的人)递解出境

ex.chText: 他曾经被流放到西伯利亚。
ex.enText: He was once banished to Siberia.

ex.chText: 格林先生被驱逐出其祖国。
ex.enText: Mr. Green was banished from his country.

synonyms.bx: 强调某国政府命令某人离开该国或其居住的地区，通常用被动语态。

d: 放逐，把…流放，把…驱逐出境

ex.chText: 签证过期后他被驱逐出西班牙。
ex.enText: He was deported from Spain when his visa expired.

ex.chText: 俄罗斯间谍被驱逐出境。

synonyms.bx: 指将违法者或无合法居住权的外国人驱逐出境。

ex.chText: 好几位反对党领导人被迫流亡意大利。
ex.enText: Several opposition leaders were exiled/banished to Italy.

ex.chText: 拿破仑曾被流放到一个岛上。
ex.enText: Napoleon was exiled/banished to an island.

synonyms.bx: 尤指因政治缘故而迫使某人流亡国外，通常用被动语态，常可与 banish 换用。

example: The poet was exiled because he signed a letter protesting the government's actions

tr: hand over to the authorities of another country
example: They extradited the fugitive to his native country so he could be tried there
They conducted themselves well during these difficult times

value.def: If a government deports someone, usually someone who is not a citizen of that country, it sends them out of the country because they have committed a crime or because it believes they do not have the right to be there.

example.ex: ...a government decision earlier this month to deport all illegal immigrants...
example.tran: 本月早些时候出台的将所有非法移民驱逐出境的政府决议

example.ex: More than 240 England football fans are being deported from Italy following riots last night.
example.tran: 昨晚的骚乱发生后有240多名英格兰球迷被驱逐出意大利。
数千名面临驱逐出境命运的阿尔巴尼亚移民

example.ex: Civil rights lawyers tried to halt the deportations.
example.tran: 民权律师试图阻止这些驱逐行为。

partsOfSpeech.dec: de 去掉 + port 拿，运 → 拿出去 → 放逐
ex 出 + port 拿，运 → 运出〔港口〕→ 出口
im 进入 + port 拿，运 → 进入〔港口〕→ 进口
port 拿，运 + able 能…的 → 能拿的 → 便携式的
port 拿，运 + age 表费用；表行为或行为的结果 → 搬运；运费
port 拿，运 + er 表名词 → 搬运工
port 拿，运 + foli 树叶，引申为页 + o 表物 → 可装运书页的东西 → 文件夹
sup 下 + port 运 → 从下面运送 → 支持
trans 转移 + port 拿，运 → 从一个地方拿到另一个地方 → 运输
ap 加强 + port 部分；分开 + ion 表动作 → 把整体分开 → 分配
dis 不 + proportion 比例 + al …的 → 不成比例的
port 部分；分开 + ion 表名词 → 部分
pro 在前 + port 部分；分开 + ion 表名词 → 按之前的量分开 →〔所占〕比例
